 <span class="floydstyle subheader">Outside the slave's hut</span>
 Nestled in the rolling hills at the outskirts of town is a small reed
 hut belonging to a captured Hittite youth. This is the slave quarters
 for a local Egyptian cattle merchant. The flimsy door to the hut is
